<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8" />
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1" />
<title>Adapt 1.0 — Adapix</title>
<meta name="description" content="Adapt 1.0. The plug-and-play AI follow-up appliance for medical practices. Stop losing six-figure cases at your front desk.">
<meta name="theme-color" content="#000000" />
<meta property="og:title" content="Adapt 1.0 — Adapix" />
<meta property="og:description" content="Front-desk magic. In a box." />
<meta property="og:image" content="/adapix_device_render.png" />
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

<style>
/* ============== RESET + PALETTE ============== */
:root{
  --bg:#000;
  --bg-card:#111;
  --bg-card-2:#1a1a1a;
  --ink:#f5f5f7;
  --ink-2:#d2d2d7;
  --ink-3:#86868b;
  --ink-4:#515154;
  --line:rgba(255,255,255,.08);
  --line-2:rgba(255,255,255,.16);
  --cyan:#00d4ff;
  --cyan-2:#60e5ff;
}
*{box-sizing:border-box;margin:0;padding:0;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent}
html{scroll-behavior:smooth;-webkit-text-size-adjust:100%}
html,body{height:100%}
body{
  font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'SF Pro Display','SF Pro Text','Inter','Helvetica Neue',Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;
  background:var(--bg);color:var(--ink);
  -webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased;-moz-osx-font-smoothing:grayscale;
  line-height:1.4;overflow-x:hidden;
}
img,svg{max-width:100%;display:block}
button,a{font:inherit;color:inherit}
button{background:transparent;border:0;cursor:pointer}
a{text-decoration:none}

/* ============== NAV — frosted glass, Apple-thin ============== */
.nav{
  position:sticky;top:0;z-index:50;height:48px;
  background:rgba(0,0,0,.72);
  backdrop-filter:saturate(180%) blur(20px);
  -webkit-backdrop-filter:saturate(180%) blur(20px);
  border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.06);
}
.nav-inner{max-width:1024px;margin:0 auto;height:100%;padding:0 22px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between}
.nav-brand{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;font-size:17px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:-.01em;color:var(--ink)}
.nav-brand .mark{
  width:22px;height:22px;border-radius:6px;
  background:linear-gradient(140deg,var(--cyan-2),var(--cyan));
  color:#001824;font-style:italic;font-weight:900;font-size:13px;
  display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;
}
.nav-links{display:flex;gap:24px}
.nav-links a{font-size:12px;font-weight:400;color:var(--ink-2);transition:color .2s}
.nav-links a:hover{color:var(--ink)}
.nav-cta{font-size:12px;color:var(--cyan-2);font-weight:500}
.nav-cta:hover{color:var(--cyan)}
@media (max-width:760px){.nav-links{display:none}}

/* ============== BUTTONS — Apple pills ============== */
.btn{
  display:inline-flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;gap:6px;
  height:44px;padding:0 22px;border-radius:980px;
  font-size:15px;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:-.005em;
  transition:background .2s,color .2s,transform .12s;cursor:pointer;
}
.btn-primary{background:var(--cyan);color:#001824;font-weight:500}
.btn-primary:hover{background:var(--cyan-2)}
.btn-link{color:var(--cyan-2);background:transparent;padding:0;height:auto}
.btn-link::after{content:"›";margin-left:4px;transition:transform .2s;display:inline-block}
.btn-link:hover{color:var(--cyan)}
.btn-link:hover::after{transform:translateX(3px)}

/* ============== TYPOGRAPHY ============== */
.eyebrow{font-size:21px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:-.005em;color:var(--cyan-2);margin-bottom:8px}
.h1{font-size:clamp(48px,8vw,116px);font-weight:600;letter-spacing:-.025em;line-height:.96;color:var(--ink)}
.h1 .lite,.h2 .lite{font-weight:300;color:var(--ink-2)}
.h2{font-size:clamp(40px,5.5vw,76px);font-weight:600;letter-spacing:-.022em;line-height:1;color:var(--ink);max-width:14ch}
.kicker{font-size:21px;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:.012em;color:var(--ink-3);margin-top:16px;max-width:30ch;line-height:1.5}
.kicker.center{margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto}
.kicker.big{font-size:24px;max-width:34ch}
.center{text-align:center}

/* ============== SECTIONS ============== */
section{position:relative}
.story{padding:120px 22px;text-align:center;border-top:1px solid var(--line)}
.story .h2{margin:0 auto 16px}
.story .kicker{margin:0 auto}
.container{max-width:1024px;margin:0 auto}

/* ============== HERO ============== */
.hero{
  padding:72px 22px 0;text-align:center;
  background:radial-gradient(ellipse at center 65%, rgba(0,212,255,.18) 0%, transparent 60%), #000;
  overflow:hidden;
}
.hero .eyebrow{font-size:24px}
.hero .h1{margin:6px auto 18px;max-width:13ch}
.hero .kicker{font-size:24px;font-weight:400;color:var(--ink-2);max-width:26ch;margin:0 auto 28px}
.hero-ctas{display:flex;gap:32px;justify-content:center;align-items:center;margin-bottom:40px;flex-wrap:wrap}
.hero-stage{
  position:relative;margin:0 auto;width:100%;max-width:780px;
  height:min(620px,68vh);
  display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;
}
@keyframes floatY{0%,100%{transform:translateY(0)}50%{transform:translateY(-16px)}}
.hero-halo{
  position:absolute;bottom:6%;left:50%;transform:translateX(-50%);
  width:55%;height:80px;border-radius:50%;
  background:radial-gradient(ellipse at center,rgba(0,212,255,.55) 0%,rgba(0,140,200,.18) 40%,transparent 70%);
  filter:blur(28px);z-index:1;
  animation:halo 7s ease-in-out infinite;
  pointer-events:none;
}

/* ============== CSS-BUILT ADAPT DEVICE ============== */
.device-wrap{position:relative;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;perspective:1200px;width:100%;height:100%;z-index:2}
.device{
  position:relative;width:min(420px,80%);aspect-ratio:1/1;transform-style:preserve-3d;
  transform:rotateX(26deg) rotateZ(-7deg);
  animation:floatY 7s ease-in-out infinite;
}
.device-body{
  position:absolute;inset:0;
  background:linear-gradient(150deg,#1c1f2e 0%,#0d1020 50%,#06080f 100%);
  clip-path:polygon(22% 0%,100% 0%,100% 100%,0% 100%,0% 50%);
  border-radius:24px;
  box-shadow:
    0 40px 100px -25px rgba(0,0,0,.85),
    inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255,255,255,.06),
    inset 0 0 0 1px rgba(0,212,255,.10);
}
.device-body::before{
  content:"";position:absolute;inset:0;
  background:linear-gradient(150deg,rgba(255,255,255,.06) 0%,transparent 30%,transparent 70%,rgba(0,212,255,.05) 100%);
  clip-path:inherit;border-radius:inherit;
}
.device-logo{
  position:absolute;left:20%;top:18%;
  font-family:Georgia,'Times New Roman',serif;
  font-style:italic;font-weight:900;font-size:46%;line-height:1;
  letter-spacing:-.04em;color:rgba(0,212,255,.82);
  text-shadow:0 0 40px rgba(0,212,255,.55),0 0 80px rgba(0,184,230,.35);
  animation:logoGlow 3.4s ease-in-out infinite;
}
@keyframes logoGlow{
  0%,100%{text-shadow:0 0 25px rgba(0,212,255,.5),0 0 50px rgba(0,184,230,.3)}
  50%   {text-shadow:0 0 50px rgba(0,212,255,.85),0 0 90px rgba(0,184,230,.5)}
}
.device-name{
  position:absolute;right:9%;bottom:14%;
  font-family:'SF Mono','JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:3.4%;letter-spacing:.2em;
  color:rgba(174,240,255,.45);text-transform:uppercase;
}
.device-oled{
  position:absolute;right:30%;bottom:8%;
  width:25%;height:7%;border-radius:5px;
  background:#040818;border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08);
  display:flex;align-items:center;padding:0 1%;
  font-family:'SF Mono','JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:2.6%;color:var(--cyan-2);
  letter-spacing:.04em;white-space:nowrap;overflow:hidden;
  box-shadow:inset 0 0 8px rgba(0,212,255,.18);
  transition:opacity .3s;
}
.device-btn{
  position:absolute;left:24%;bottom:6%;
  width:3.5%;aspect-ratio:1/1;border-radius:50%;
  background:radial-gradient(circle,rgba(0,212,255,.95),rgba(0,184,230,.3));
  box-shadow:0 0 14px var(--cyan);animation:pulseDot 2.8s ease-in-out infinite;
}
@keyframes pulseDot{0%,100%{box-shadow:0 0 8px var(--cyan)}50%{box-shadow:0 0 18px var(--cyan),0 0 32px rgba(0,184,230,.5)}}
.device-underglow{
  position:absolute;left:50%;bottom:-2%;
  width:72%;height:14%;
  background:radial-gradient(ellipse at center top,
    rgba(0,212,255,.85) 0%,rgba(0,184,230,.4) 30%,transparent 70%);
  filter:blur(16px);transform:translateX(-50%);
  border-radius:50%;animation:underglow 3.4s ease-in-out infinite;
  pointer-events:none;
}
@keyframes underglow{0%,100%{opacity:.7}50%{opacity:1}}
@keyframes halo{0%,100%{opacity:.6;transform:translateX(-50%) scale(1)}50%{opacity:1;transform:translateX(-50%) scale(1.08)}}

/* ============== STORY VISUAL ============== */
.story-stage{
  position:relative;margin:80px auto 0;width:100%;max-width:680px;
  height:min(520px,60vh);
  display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;
}
.story-stage .product-img{height:90%}
.story-stage .hero-halo{width:50%;height:60px;bottom:8%}

/* ============== TILES ============== */
.tiles{padding:60px 22px 120px;border-top:1px solid var(--line)}
.tiles-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:14px;max-width:1024px;margin:0 auto}
@media(max-width:760px){.tiles-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr}}
.tile{
  background:var(--bg-card);border-radius:22px;padding:60px 44px;
  min-height:480px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;justify-content:space-between;
  position:relative;overflow:hidden;border:1px solid var(--line);
}
.tile.big{grid-column:span 2;flex-direction:row;align-items:center;gap:40px;min-height:380px}
@media(max-width:760px){.tile.big{flex-direction:column;grid-column:span 1}}
.tile h3{font-size:30px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:-.015em;line-height:1.1;color:var(--ink);margin-bottom:12px}
.tile p{font-size:16.5px;color:var(--ink-3);line-height:1.5;max-width:38ch}
.tile-visual{margin-top:32px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;flex:1;min-height:160px}
.tile.big .tile-visual{margin-top:0;flex:1}
.tile.big > div:first-child{flex:1}

/* Mini "screen" widget */
.mini-screen{
  background:#0a0d18;border:1px solid var(--line-2);border-radius:14px;
  padding:16px 18px;width:100%;max-width:300px;
  font-family:'SF Mono','JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:12px;color:var(--cyan-2);
  line-height:1.7;text-align:left;
  box-shadow:0 0 28px -4px rgba(0,212,255,.3) inset;
}
.mini-screen .row{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;color:var(--ink-2)}
.mini-screen .row.dim{color:var(--ink-4)}
.mini-screen .row span:last-child{color:var(--cyan-2)}

/* Battery bar */
.battery-bar{
  width:220px;height:32px;border-radius:9px;border:2px solid var(--ink-3);
  position:relative;padding:3px;display:flex;align-items:center;
}
.battery-bar::after{content:"";position:absolute;right:-7px;top:50%;transform:translateY(-50%);width:5px;height:16px;background:var(--ink-3);border-radius:0 3px 3px 0}
.battery-bar .fill{width:84%;height:100%;background:linear-gradient(90deg,#34c759,#30d158);border-radius:5px;box-shadow:0 0 20px rgba(52,199,89,.5)}
.battery-label{font-family:'SF Mono','JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:14px;color:var(--ink-2);margin-top:14px}

/* Tile product image (smaller version) */
.tile-product{
  width:auto;height:200px;object-fit:contain;
  filter:drop-shadow(0 30px 40px rgba(0,160,220,.35));
  animation:floatY 7s ease-in-out infinite;
}

/* ============== SPECS ============== */
.specs{padding:120px 22px;background:#0a0a0a;text-align:center;border-top:1px solid var(--line);border-bottom:1px solid var(--line)}
.specs .h2{margin:0 auto 56px}
.spec-grid{
  display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr);gap:1px;
  background:var(--line);border-radius:18px;overflow:hidden;
  max-width:1024px;margin:0 auto;
}
@media(max-width:880px){.spec-grid{grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr)}}
@media(max-width:520px){.spec-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr}}
.spec{background:var(--bg-card-2);padding:36px 24px}
.spec .n{font-size:32px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:-.015em;color:var(--ink);line-height:1.05}
.spec .l{font-size:13.5px;font-weight:400;color:var(--ink-3);margin-top:12px;line-height:1.4}

/* ============== PRICING ============== */
.pricing{padding:120px 22px;text-align:center;border-top:1px solid var(--line)}
.pricing .h2{margin:0 auto 24px}
.price-card{
  max-width:480px;margin:60px auto 0;
  background:var(--bg-card);border:1px solid var(--line-2);
  border-radius:22px;padding:44px 36px 36px;text-align:center;
}
.price-card .device{font-size:14px;color:var(--ink-3);font-weight:500;letter-spacing:.02em;text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:8px}
.price-card .name{font-size:24px;font-weight:600;color:var(--ink);margin-bottom:20px;letter-spacing:-.01em}
.price-card .amount{font-size:64px;font-weight:600;color:var(--ink);letter-spacing:-.025em;line-height:1}
.price-card .unit{font-size:18px;color:var(--ink-3);font-weight:400;margin-left:6px}
.price-card .plus{margin-top:18px;font-size:15px;color:var(--ink-2)}
.price-card .plus b{color:var(--ink);font-weight:600}
.price-card .footnote{font-size:12.5px;color:var(--ink-4);margin-top:18px;line-height:1.5}
.price-card .btn{margin-top:28px;width:100%}

/* ============== BUY BANNER ============== */
.buy-banner{background:#000;padding:140px 22px;text-align:center;border-top:1px solid var(--line)}
.buy-banner .eyebrow{font-size:21px}
.buy-banner h2{font-size:clamp(40px,6vw,78px);font-weight:600;letter-spacing:-.022em;line-height:1.02;margin:6px auto 22px;max-width:18ch;color:var(--ink)}
.buy-banner .kicker{font-size:21px;margin:0 auto 36px;max-width:32ch}
.buy-ctas{display:flex;gap:28px;justify-content:center;align-items:center;flex-wrap:wrap}

/* Reservation form */
.reserve-form{
  max-width:440px;margin:0 auto;padding-top:30px;
  display:flex;gap:10px;flex-wrap:wrap;justify-content:center;
}
.reserve-form input{
  flex:1;min-width:220px;
  background:#0a0a0a;border:1px solid var(--line-2);
  border-radius:980px;height:44px;padding:0 22px;
  color:var(--ink);font-size:15px;font-family:inherit;outline:none;
}
.reserve-form input:focus{border-color:rgba(0,212,255,.5);box-shadow:0 0 0 3px rgba(0,212,255,.15)}
.reserve-success{
  display:none;margin-top:30px;font-size:16px;color:#30d158;
  padding:14px 18px;border-radius:12px;
  background:rgba(48,209,88,.1);border:1px solid rgba(48,209,88,.35);
  max-width:440px;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto;
}
.reserve-success.on{display:block}

/* ============== FOOTER ============== */
footer{background:#0a0a0a;padding:36px 22px 22px;border-top:1px solid var(--line);color:var(--ink-4);font-size:12px}
.footer-inner{max-width:1024px;margin:0 auto}
.footer-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:40px;padding-bottom:22px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--line)}
@media(max-width:760px){.footer-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr;gap:24px}}
.footer-col h4{font-size:12px;font-weight:600;color:var(--ink-2);margin-bottom:10px}
.footer-col a{display:block;color:var(--ink-4);font-size:12px;padding:4px 0;transition:color .2s;line-height:1.5}
.footer-col a:hover{color:var(--ink-2)}
.footer-fine{padding:22px 0 0;display:flex;justify-content:space-between;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:14px}
.footer-fine p{font-size:12px;color:var(--ink-4)}

/* ============== SCROLL REVEAL ============== */
.reveal{opacity:0;transform:translateY(28px);transition:opacity .8s ease,transform .9s cubic-bezier(.2,.7,.2,1)}
.reveal.in{opacity:1;transform:translateY(0)}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- ===== NAV ===== -->
<nav class="nav">
  <div class="nav-inner">
    <a href="#" class="nav-brand"><div class="mark">A</div>Adapix</a>
    <div class="nav-links">
      <a href="#adapt">Adapt 1.0</a>
      <a href="#features">Features</a>
      <a href="#specs">Tech Specs</a>
      <a href="#pricing">Pricing</a>
    </div>
    <a href="#reserve" class="nav-cta">Reserve →</a>
  </div>
</nav>

<!-- ===== HERO ===== -->
<section class="hero" id="adapt">
  <div class="eyebrow">Adapt 1.0</div>
  <h1 class="h1">Real AI.<br><span class="lite">In your practice.<br>Today.</span></h1>
  <p class="kicker">The simplest way to bring AI into how your practice already runs. Plug it in. Tell it about you. Let it work alongside your team.</p>
  <div class="hero-ctas">
    <a href="#reserve" class="btn btn-primary">Reserve yours</a>
    <a href="#features" class="btn btn-link">Learn more</a>
  </div>
  <div class="hero-stage">
    <div class="hero-halo"></div>
    <div class="device-wrap">
      <div class="device">
        <div class="device-body">
          <div class="device-logo">A</div>
          <div class="device-name">Adapt 1.0</div>
          <div class="device-oled" id="oled1">Adapix · idle</div>
          <div class="device-btn"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="device-underglow"></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ===== STORY 1: REAL COMPUTER ===== -->
<section class="story" id="features">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="eyebrow reveal">On-premise intelligence</div>
    <h2 class="h2 center reveal" style="margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto">AI on your desk.<br><span class="lite">Not in someone<br>else's cloud.</span></h2>
    <p class="kicker center reveal">The AI runs inside the device, on your office network. No cloud account to manage. No vendor lock-in. No monthly SaaS that turns off when a credit card expires. Just a smart box that joins your team — and stays.</p>
    <div class="story-stage reveal">
      <div class="hero-halo"></div>
      <div class="device-wrap">
        <div class="device">
          <div class="device-body">
            <div class="device-logo">A</div>
            <div class="device-name">Adapt 1.0</div>
            <div class="device-oled">8GB · 1TB · Pi5</div>
            <div class="device-btn"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="device-underglow"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ===== STORY 2: LIGHT + DISPLAY ===== -->
<section class="story">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="eyebrow reveal">Always present</div>
    <h2 class="h2 center reveal" style="margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto">An assistant<br><span class="lite">you can see<br>working.</span></h2>
    <p class="kicker center reveal">The box glows cyan when Adapix is composing. The OLED shows what she's working on. The Circuit-A logo lights up when there's something for you to look at. AI you don't have to open an app to check in on — just glance at the desk.</p>
    <div class="story-stage reveal">
      <div class="hero-halo"></div>
      <div class="device-wrap">
        <div class="device">
          <div class="device-body">
            <div class="device-logo">A</div>
            <div class="device-name">Adapt 1.0</div>
            <div class="device-oled" id="oled2">Maria K. needs you</div>
            <div class="device-btn"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="device-underglow"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ===== TILES ===== -->
<section class="tiles">
  <div class="tiles-grid">

    <div class="tile reveal">
      <div>
        <h3>Configure it<br>by talking<br>to it.</h3>
        <p>Tell Adapix what your practice cares about — in plain English, the same way you'd brief a new hire. "We focus on wisdom teeth on Tuesdays." "Send recall reminders in Spanish for our south-side patients." The dashboard shapes itself around what you say. You never touch a settings page.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="tile-visual">
        <div class="mini-screen">
          <div class="row"><span>Unscheduled referrals</span><span>14</span></div>
          <div class="row"><span>Recall this week</span><span>6</span></div>
          <div class="row dim"><span>Post-op check-ins</span><span>off</span></div>
          <div class="row"><span>Financing follow-ups</span><span>3</span></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="tile reveal" style="transition-delay:.08s">
      <div>
        <h3>Always on.<br>Always present.</h3>
        <p>Internal UPS battery. Cellular failover for SMS. Adapt stays online through power flickers, Wi-Fi outages, and weekend storms — the same way the lights in your office do. Reliability you can build a workflow on.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="tile-visual" style="flex-direction:column">
        <div class="battery-bar"><div class="fill"></div></div>
        <div class="battery-label">8 hr 12 min · 84%</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="tile big reveal">
      <div>
        <h3>Five minutes<br>to set up.<br>A new team member by tomorrow.</h3>
        <p>No IT consultant. No four-week onboarding. No 80-question setup wizard you abandon halfway. Plug in the ethernet, open the URL on your phone, and Adapix asks about your practice the way a thoughtful new hire would. By the time you walk in tomorrow morning, she's already part of the team.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="tile-visual">
